  "title": "[FEB START!]🤩Junior Sales Development Associate- office hours/travelling opportunities",
  "description": "<p>Are you Bold, innovative, and passionate about connecting people with products, sales are in your DNA!</p>\n<p><strong>You are the \"hunter\" we are looking for...</strong></p>\n<p>As a Junior Sales Representative, at A.scend International,</p>\n<p>you will be responsible for executing key sales and business development initiatives including</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>driving sales</li>\n  <li>creating new customer relationships</li>\n  <li>identifying, establishing, and qualifying all leads</li>\n  <li>following up with leads, arranging appointments to close sales</li>\n  <li>able to effectively communicate the features and benefits of solutions</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>What Can You Expect</strong></p>\n<p><em>Career Development</em></p>\n<p>we invest in your growth, giving every individual the chance to hone and learn new skills</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><em>Personal Development</em></p>\n<p>We value individuals, providing regular development, workshops and networking sessions to support the learning process</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><em>Traveling Opportunities</em></p>\n<p>We need you to have min. 6 months validity for your passport so that you can join us in visiting and learning from the various countries.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><em>Great environment culture</em></p>\n<p>We value and support providing a teamwork environment by giving 1 on 1 feedback and coaching sessions.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>What We Expect</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Willing and coachable</li>\n  <li>Able to be on the frontline meeting customer face to face</li>\n  <li>Passionate</li>\n  <li>Optimistic and Resilient. Knowing that after meeting the 'no' there could be a yes, and not allowing negative responses to bring you down.</li>\n  <li>Great communicator</li>\n  <li>Student mentality. Like a 'learning' sponge, asking questions to develop skill sets and knowledge</li>\n  <li>Bilingual. We are mostly dealing with Chinese-speaking clients</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Send your updated resume now</strong></p>",
